{"tid":2022523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區議員向考評局下跪","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:45:38.000Z","uid":146030,"like":14,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d710b54415aca9dd090f40404098b054791dc8ec","tid":2022523,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄早前批評本屆中學文憑試中，一道有關「日本侵華」的試題傷害同胞感情且有引導性，要求考評局取消該試題。<br />\n<br />\n北區區議員、中文補習老師蔣旻正收集過萬個聯署，並於今日到考評局外下跪，要求局方拒絕取消有關試題，並譴責教育局楊潤雄以政治手段干預。<br />\n<br />\n蔣旻正指，今屆考生早已在考試前經歷反送中、武漢肺炎疫情等事，未料考試結束後仍需要對教育局的政治干預。他形容教育局已經「淪陷」，考評局是「最後一道防線」，促考評局秘書長蘇國生在楊潤雄面前「唔好跪」。<br />\n<br />\n蘇國生未有現身，最終由局方代表接收聯署信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=2968593459844339&amp;set=a.321611837875861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D2968593459844339%26set%3Da.321611837875861&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=12b2d835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=2968593459844339&amp;set=a.321611837875861</a><br />\n<br />\n你跪咩撚嘢呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尊嚴去咗邊?"},{"pid":"c965b9ce527f883b61c7099ef349a4d3047392c0","tid":2022523,"uid":177213,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLumWHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLumWHO.png&h=d82511a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guTyNPu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguTyNPu.png&h=ca6bb22c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6deb36c43307c195e22a287d55a6e732008c2f60","tid":2022523,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"一個要人下跪政權仲邊有尊嚴"},{"pid":"4d2d05d9d6d08f8ea2669fa52d88ceb6cb2d7197","tid":2022523,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6deb36c43307